data.description: Discover this exquisite residence featuring 3 bedrooms and 1.5 baths situated on a generous .72-acre lot, boasting the absence of an HOA. Recently renovated in 2022, this home showcases a modern aesthetic with new kitchen cabinets, granite countertops, sink, lighting fixtures, windows, roof, laminate floors, bathroom vanities, sinks, plumbing, electrical breakers, and more. The expansive deck offers panoramic views of the spacious fenced backyard, carport, and storage area. Ideally positioned near schools, shopping, restaurants, I-20 interstate, medical facilities, and more. Playset will be taken down.
